Text:
This torrent might end.  Read this article in the Wall Street Journal:

http://online.wsj.com/article/SB120001282486582581.html?mod=todays_us_nonsub_marketplace

While it still might happen, the article, written back in January of 2008, has so far not accurately prediced the doom of TPB.  There were some small glitches early on, but, as you can see, we are still sharing!  Long live TPB and all the others like them!
